All my life, I've bought and owned nothing but 2-seater sports cars.</p><p>
Why?</p><p>
Not that I care what other people think as I drive by...I generally don't notice that, but I do so because they are FUN to drive to me. I like having a vehicle with good performance and I like the looks of them.</p><p>
Whereas a lot of people only look at a car as something to get from point A to B<span class="substr"> </span></p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64278872">

</div>
